		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">构型械驻于原地，于自身处缓慢产生2次雷暴脉冲，均造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害；与此同时2枚浮游炮发射迂回中央的测距激光，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">远离构型械时，其将发射持续的雷激光，持续造成<span color="#ffacff">40%,20%,12%,4%,0.4%</span><span>伤害；若在发射激光时靠近构型械，则其立即停止激光发射，转而化为爪掌拍下，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">构型械驻于原地，于自身炮筒发射3枚雷轰弹，落地爆炸，每枚造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害，并留下雷地面，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">7%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">过于靠近构型械时，构型械化作巨星爪掌并拍下，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害，同时产生6道纵方向中心合拢的激光，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，聚拢后发生爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">过于靠近构型械时，构型械化作巨星爪掌并划扫，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害；此后浮游炮接着发射弹雨，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">30%,15%,3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1247" width="1014" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「应战对策」满后优先施放，构型械横过来，并使用7枚浮游炮组装发射半圆形激光，呈顺时针旋转，接触激光持续造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。<br/>在另外一半扇形区域内，玩家将会持续获得燃素，且造成的伤害提升</span><span color="#ffcebf">5%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="1015" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">构型械开掘出2柱<span textDecoration="underline">固态燃素</span><span>，其上有「</span><span textDecoration="underline">汲聚械</span><span>」存在，辅助构型械进行蓄力；蓄力期间的浮游炮不断发射激光，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，并留下造成</span><span color="#ffacff">10%</span><span>伤害的滞留雷息；15s后，构型械丢出球状雷弹，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>在场非无敌状态角色。<br/>「应战对策」满后施放，若为此法触发，则在「扫彻方隅」结束后，浮游炮会利用雷激光规划开采场地，激光造成</span><span color="#ffacff">30%</span><span>伤害；若构型械不发生转身，则固态燃素将出现在激光交点处。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7火力升级套件.assets/Image_14.png')" x="722" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/秘源机兵%B7火力升级套件.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1192" width="442" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">固态燃素：无法直接攀爬，比一般构型械的高一倍，仅「回声之子」成员可直接攀爬。<br/>「汲聚械」：进入屏障内以1次攻击击破，屏障外免疫，击破全部可使构型械瘫痪12s，并扣除其<span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
